 significantly enhanced compared to most past\nestimates. We find that thermal models with p-wave annihilation may be within\nrange of detection in the near future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Nov 2021 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Apr 2022 00:00:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-20"}
